{"tid":863900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷工/罷坐？不了.....外國人選擇跳閘","createTime":"2018-10-16T01:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T05:19:07.000Z","uid":169992,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"812fb117d292a4395f9de35e1f93050f3b162fa0","tid":863900,"uid":169992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:32:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1037687\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1037687&d=nE4dWvOceGSz5OMKEp7B1kkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=d26b69e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1037687&h=d4008936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1037687</a><br />\n<br />\n最後就是跳閘。如果你覺得不付車資跳閘很激進，或者覺得只有大陸人會這樣做，不要怕，我相信絕大部份香港人與你想法都一樣，同時也不認為跳閘會在香港流行起來。有趣的是，如果我們於七十年代正值香港不合作運動當中討論跳閘，大家關注的可能就會是如何安全不被抓住，而不是應不應該做。英語世界專有名詞叫做fare dodger，意即「避票者」，歐美各地都有。比較有名的例子有明星作家Russell Brand。因為跳閘的是名人(大概像香港的黃子華跳閘)，大眾也議論紛紛，有人說他教壞細路，也有人說制裁鐵路公司相當合理。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">三年前嘅文章，<br />\n狗鐵繼續可加可減、繼續壞車。<br />\n我哋繼續養肥佢，而嘜都做唔到/嘜都唔做？<br />\n跳閘？不了</span>"},{"pid":"689aa304fe9cf90f7013d479533458070252dee5","tid":863900,"uid":106336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T17:32:19.000Z","msg":"睇嚟依家終於有用"},{"pid":"c093471a4c327b12b57701e2b0b6f3c1c8024b8d","tid":863900,"uid":169992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"689aa304fe9cf90f7013d479533458070252dee5","tid":863900,"uid":106336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T17:32:19.000Z","msg":"睇嚟依家終於有用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T17:33:47.000Z","msg":"上年10月開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b504a892174f596d3db9f60745a6f27b737dbd40","tid":863900,"uid":106336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c093471a4c327b12b57701e2b0b6f3c1c8024b8d","tid":863900,"uid":169992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"689aa304fe9cf90f7